  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    io.github.prolobjectlink.db.entity.EntityClass.compile()
    Use generator method and compile with io.github.prolobjectlink.web.compiler.ModelCompiler. This method compile fine but remove entity not work fine because raise an exception.
    io.github.prolobjectlink.db.jpa.spi.JPAPersistenceXmlParser.parsePersistenceXml(URL)
    Use PersistenceXmlParser instead.
    io.github.prolobjectlink.web.io.ServerFile.toURL()
    This method does not automatically escape characters that are illegal in URLs. It is recommended that new code convert an abstract pathname into a URL by first converting it into a URI, via the toURI method, and then converting the URI into a URL via the URI.toURL method.
